    "temperature": "number",
    "humidite": "number",
    "datMesure": "string (ISO 8601)"
  }
]
```

### GET /api/entrepot/:id/lots
**Description**: Liste des lots stockés triés par datSto croissante (FIFO)

**Headers**: `Authorization: Bearer <token>`

**Response (200)**:
```json
[
  {
    "idLotGrains": "string",
    "idEntrepot": "string",
    "datSto": "string (ISO 8601)",
    "statut": "string",
    "datSortie": "string (ISO 8601, nullable)"
  }
]
```

### POST /api/entrepot/:id/lots
**Description**: Créer un nouveau lot dans cet entrepôt

**Headers**: `Authorization: Bearer <token>`

**Request Body**:
```json
